Package schedule

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Course
    Represents a single course, including name, days and time scheduled.
    CourseList
    Represents a list of courses, does little besides reading them in from a data file and storing them in an accessible manner.
    Schedule
    Class that holds a number of courses that do not conflict and can print out a simple day-by-day schedule.
    ScheduleMaker
    Interactive schedule maker.
